hopobject.body: Hold the line, please china brush machine Estimates for how much the low-mileage vehicles will sell for are impossible, according to Yvette VanDerBrink, whose auction house is running the sale. "We cannot guess price – because there is no comparison. Anything that is well advertised with active bidding will bring what the market is [willing to pay] – we firmly believe that and work for our sellers. This is their lives and life’s work."
